<td>Constant O(1)</td>
<td>Linear O(n)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Memory</strong></td>
<td>Minimal</td>
<td>All rows in RAM</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>When to use each</strong>:
- <code>func.count()</code>: Just need count, large dataset
- <code>len()</code>: Already fetched data, need objects anyway</p>
