<p><strong>Q99: Logic: Maintainability Index.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Complete Answer</strong>:
Our code:
-   Short functions? Yes.
-   Descriptive names? Yes (<code>send_booking_confirmation_email</code> vs <code>mail()</code>).
-   Comments? Yes.
High maintainability.</p>
