<p><strong>Complete Answer</strong>:
The <strong>Stability</strong>.
By handling edge cases (invalid IDs, CSRF, Types) and simple structure, the backend runs reliably. It connects the Complex Database Logic (Shiva) with the Frontend needs (Parent) indistinguishably.</p>
